INUMBER 982
NAME 319
ARMOR
WORN_HANDS
WEIGHT 4
VOLUME 2
ARTICLE SOME
VARIABLE olenka
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Silver and gold streaks swirl throughout the surface of the dark metal,
outlining the raised depictions tall mountain peaks that are engraved on
the backs of the gauntlets.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFITEM -1 WORN
    ADD olenka 1
     IFVAR olenka < 21
       ECHO PLAYER You feel the strength of the mountains rush through your body!
       ECHO OTHERS %N vibrates with the awe-inspiring strength of the mountains themselves!
       SPELL 209 50
     ENDIF
      IFVAR olenka => 21
        ECHO PLAYER The gauntlets glow dimly, but their power seems spent for the day.
        ECHO OTHERS %N's gauntlets glow dimly for a moment.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
